                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_back_problem__c != '' &&
                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_back_problem__c == 'YES' , true, false)}"/></p>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="Tablebackgroundcolor">
              <td class="CustomColspanTd" colspan="2">
                  <span style="color:white;">Section 5 – Medical History Declaration (Part 2) </span><br/>
                  <span style="color:white;">第五部分 – 健康狀況 (第二節)</span>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
              <td class="CustomTd_title">
                  <p>Apart from the conditions that aforementioned, is person insured currently receiving or have been advised to seek any medical advice or treatment (other than for minor conditions such as cold or flu) or awaiting the results of any test/ investigation since the application date of the above policy?</p>
                  <p>除上述已告知的狀況外，由上述保單申請日期到現在受保人是否現正或<br/>曾被建議接受任何醫療諮詢或醫藥治療（輕微狀況如：傷風、<br/>感冒除外）或受保人是否現正等候任何檢驗或診斷結果？</p>
              </td>
              <td class="CustomTd" align="left" valign="top">
                  <apex:outputText value="{!CASE( policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_apart_from_con__c, 
                                                 'YES','YES<br/>是' , 
                                                 'NO','NO<br/>否' ,  '')}" escape="false" />
                  <p><apex:outputField value="{!policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_apart_from_con_details__c}" 
                                       rendered="{!IF(policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_apart_from_con__c != null &&
                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_apart_from_con__c != '' &&
                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_apart_from_con__c == 'YES' , true, false)}"/></p>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="Tablebackgroundcolor">
              <td class="CustomColspanTd" colspan="2">
                  <span style="color:white;">Section 6 – Family History Declaration</span><br/>
                  <span style="color:white;">第六部分 – 家族病史</span>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
              <td class="CustomTd_title">
                  <p>Has person insured’s biological mother, father, or any sister or brother been diagnosed prior to age 60 with any of the following?</p>
                  <p>Cancer, heart disease, stroke, diabetes, polycystic kidney disease, Alzheimer’s disease or any other inherited disease or disorder.</p>
                  <p>受保人的親生父母、兄弟姊妹是否於六十歲前被診斷患有以下疾病？</p>
                  <p>癌症、心臟疾病、中風、糖尿病、多囊性腎病、亞爾茲默氏病<br/>或其他任何遺傳疾病或功能失常。</p>
              </td>
              <td class="CustomTd" align="left" valign="top">
                  <apex:outputText value="{!CASE( policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_members_disease__c, 
                                                 'YES','YES<br/>是' , 
                                                 'NO','NO<br/>否' ,  '')}" escape="false" />
                  <p><apex:outputField value="{!policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_members_disease_details__c}" 
                                       rendered="{!IF(policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_members_disease__c != null &&
                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_members_disease__c != '' &&
                                      policyChangeRequestInfo.Reinstatement_members_disease__c == 'YES' , true, false)}"/></p>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="Tablebackgroundcolor">
              <td class="CustomColspanTd" colspan="2">
                  <span style="color:white;">Declaration &amp; Authorization</span><br/>
                  <span style="color:white;">聲明及授權</span>
              </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
             <td class="CustomColspanTd" colspan="2">
                 <div style="width:100% ; word-wrap: break-word;word-break: break-all;">
                     <!--JOBR-184: JOBR-199/226 updated by Kermit at 20221012-->
